'''人民動員'''（{{lang-ar|الحشد الشعبي}}；{{lang-en|Popular Mobilization Forces}}）是一個得到[[伊拉克|伊拉克]]政府支持的[[民兵|民兵]]整合組織，初期由約40個幾乎全是[[什葉派|什葉派]]的民兵團體組成。<ref>{{cite news|title=Islamic State: The caliphate strikes back|url=http://www.economist.com/news/middle-east-and-africa/21651762-fall-ramadi-shows-islamic-state-still-business-caliphate-strikes-back|accessdate=25 May 2015|work=The Economist|date=23 May 2015|archive-date=2017-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171009215911/https://www.economist.com/news/middle-east-and-africa/21651762-fall-ramadi-shows-islamic-state-still-business-caliphate-strikes-back|dead-url=no}}</ref>「人民動員」是為了抗擊[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]而於2014年6月建立，從當時已存在的民兵武裝整合而成，隸屬於伊拉克內政部的「人民動員委員會」。

在伊斯蘭國崛起後，由於當時的伊拉克政府軍普遍缺乏戰意，無力獨自抗擊伊斯蘭國，「人民動員」成為伊拉克政府倚賴的一支重要地面武裝力量。另一方面，「人民動員」被指與[[伊朗|伊朗]]關係密切，接受伊朗軍事顧問訓練甚至由他們指揮。<ref name=cnn20150311>{{Cite news |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2015/03/11/middleeast/lister-iraq-iran/ |title=Battle for Tikrit: Despite billions in aid, Iraqi army relies on militia, and Iran |work=CNN.com |date=2015-03-11 |accessdate=2015-07-31 |archive-date=2019-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190516044124/https://edition.cnn.com/2015/03/11/middleeast/lister-iraq-iran/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>伊拉克的[[遜尼派|遜尼派]]普遍對什葉派的「人民動員」有疑慮，不大願意讓他們進駐遜尼派地區。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://cn.nytimes.com/world/20150408/c08anbar/dual/ |title=宗派疑虑考验伊拉克政府军西进决策 |work=纽约时报中文网 |date=2015-04-08 |accessdate=2015-07-31 |archive-date=2021-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106213255/https://cn.nytimes.com/world/20150408/c08anbar/dual/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

據2016年報道，伊拉克政府每年向民兵組織提供約14億美元經費。<ref name=bbc35998716/>2016年12月19日，伊拉克總統[[福阿德·马苏姆|福阿德·马苏姆]]批准一項把「人民動員」納入國家武裝部隊的法律，該法律已於11月在議會獲得通過。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://mobile.almasdarnews.com/article/law-passes-making-pmu-part-iraqs-national-forces/|script-title=en:Law passes making the PMU a part of Iraq’s national forces.|accessdate=2017-10-24|archive-date=2017-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171015155912/https://mobile.almasdarnews.com/article/law-passes-making-pmu-part-iraqs-national-forces/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2018年3月，伊拉克總理[[海德尔·阿巴迪|海德尔·阿巴迪]]宣佈將「人民動員」收編入安全部隊，受國防部管轄。<ref name=xh20180310/>

==成立==
伊斯蘭國於2014年6月10日攻佔[[摩蘇爾|摩蘇爾]]後，伊拉克什葉派[[大阿亞圖拉|大阿亞圖拉]][[阿里·西斯塔尼|阿里·西斯塔尼]]於6月13日發佈教令，呼籲信眾保衛什葉派聖地和[[巴格達|巴格達]]，以及加入反攻伊斯蘭國。<ref>{{cite news|last1=al Khadimi|first1=Mustafa|title=Will Sistani be able to control popular mobilization forces?|url=http://www.al-monitor.com/pulse/originals/2015/03/iraq-sistani-righteous-jihad-fatwa-popular-mobilization.html|work=Al-Monitor|date=12 March 2015|accessdate=14 March 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150313111104/http://www.al-monitor.com/pulse/originals/2015/03/iraq-sistani-righteous-jihad-fatwa-popular-mobilization.html|archivedate=2015年3月13日}}</ref>他的呼籲得到許多什葉派教徒響應，「人民動員」隨後成立。

「人民動員」的出現，據報使戰場形勢有了基本轉變，削弱伊斯蘭國在[[游擊戰|游擊戰]]和[[心理戰|心理戰]]方面的優勢。<ref name="al-monitor.com">{{cite news|last1=al-Khadimi|first1=Mustafa|title=Iraqi volunteers' victories don't justify atrocities|url=http://www.al-monitor.com/pulse/en/contents/articles/originals/2014/12/iraq-popular-mobilization-shiite-achievements-violations.html|accessdate=14 March 2015|work=al-Monitor|date=22 December 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402134304/http://www.al-monitor.com/pulse/en/contents/articles/originals/2014/12/iraq-popular-mobilization-shiite-achievements-violations.html|archivedate=2015年4月2日|df=}}</ref>

==成員==
至今未有「人民動員」兵力的官方數字公佈，對於總人數的估計，少則6萬至9萬人，<!--<ref name=Niqash />-->多則有10萬至12萬人（2015年初），<ref>{{cite news|last1=Sly|first1=Liz|script-title=en:Pro-Iran militias’ success in Iraq could undermine U.S.|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/iraqs-pro-iranian-shiite-militias-lead-the-war-against-the-islamic-state/2015/02/15/5bbb1cf0-ac94-11e4-8876-460b1144cbc1_story.html|accessdate=22 March 2015|work=The Washington Post|date=15 February 2015|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122172147/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/iraqs-pro-iranian-shiite-militias-lead-the-war-against-the-islamic-state/2015/02/15/5bbb1cf0-ac94-11e4-8876-460b1144cbc1_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>包括1000至3000名遜尼派戰士。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Wright|first1=Robin|script-title=en:In War Against ISIS, Numbers Don’t Always Tell the Story|url=http://blogs.wsj.com/washwire/2015/03/13/in-war-against-isis-numbers-dont-always-tell-the-story/|publisher=The Wall Street Journal|accessdate=23 March 2015|date=13 March 2015|archive-date=2021-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108043414/https://blogs.wsj.com/washwire/2015/03/13/in-war-against-isis-numbers-dont-always-tell-the-story/|dead-url=no}}</ref>由伊拉克基督教徒組成的「巴比倫旅」也是「人民動員」成員之一。<ref name=bbc35998716>{{Cite news |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/magazine-35998716 |title=The Christian militia fighting IS |work=BBC News |date=2016-04-11 |accessdate=2016-04-26 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126133524/https://www.bbc.com/news/magazine-35998716 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==武器裝備==
伊拉克政府被指把美國提供的武器裝備轉發給「人民動員」，此外伊朗也被指是「人民動員」的主要武器供應者。據報伊朗在2014年向伊拉克出售了價值近100億美元的武器和設備。除此之外，伊朗也持續向伊拉克提供伊朗武器，<ref>{{cite news|last1=Hemdawi|first1=Hamza|last2=Abdul-Zahra|first2=Qassim|title=Iran eclipses U.S. as Iraq's ally in fight against militants|url=http://www.militarytimes.com/story/military/2015/01/12/iran-iraq-militants/21623533/|accessdate=20 March 2015|work=MilitaryTimes|date=12 January 2015|archive-date=2016-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161027030019/http://www.militarytimes.com/story/military/2015/01/12/iran-iraq-militants/21623533/|dead-url=no}}</ref>包括伊朗製的反坦克炮和迫擊炮。<ref>{{cite web|title=Better pay, better weapons: Are Shiite militias growing more powerful than Iraqi army?|url=http://www.preemptivelove.org/better_pay_better_weapons_are_shiite_militias_growing_more_powerful_than_iraqi_army|publisher=Preemptive Love Coalition|accessdate=23 March 2015|date=31 January 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402095749/http://www.preemptivelove.org/better_pay_better_weapons_are_shiite_militias_growing_more_powerful_than_iraqi_army|archivedate=2015年4月2日}}</ref>

2015年5月，美國開始向伊拉克政府付運約值16億美元的軍備。據報已運抵的武器大多落入「人民動員」手上。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Enders|first1=David|title=US Starts Sending $1.6 Billion Worth of Promised Arms to Iraq — But Who Will Get Them?|url=https://news.vice.com/topic/popular-mobilization-forces|accessdate=21 June 2015|work=Vice News|date=6 June 2015|archive-date=2017-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171009171128/https://news.vice.com/topic/popular-mobilization-forces|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==參與戰役==
比較重要的有2015年3月的[[第二次提克里特之戰|收復提克里特之戰]]。<ref>{{cite news|title=Mobilization forces hand over security affairs to local police in Tikrit|url=http://www.iraqtradelinknews.com/2015/04/mobilization-forces-hand-over-security.html|accessdate=15 April 2015|agency=Iraq Tradelink News Agency|date=4 April 2015|archive-date=2020-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200522005823/http://www.iraqtradelinknews.com/2015/04/mobilization-forces-hand-over-security.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2015年4月6日，伊拉克總理[[海德尔·阿巴迪|海德尔·阿巴迪]]表示「人民動員」不會參與[[解放摩蘇爾|收復摩蘇爾]]的行動。不過到2016年10月[[摩蘇爾之戰|摩蘇爾之戰]]開始後，「人民動員」於10月29日派出5,000名民兵在[[摩蘇爾|摩蘇爾]]以西攻擊伊斯蘭國。「人民動員」表示他們不會進入以遜尼派居民為主的摩蘇爾城內。<ref name=xh20161101>{{Cite news |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2016-11/01/c_129344381.htm |title=什叶派民兵现身摩苏尔战场 土耳其有意见 |publisher=新華網 |date=2016-11-01 |accessdate=2017-01-16 |archive-date=2017-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170409181340/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2016-11/01/c_129344381.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

「人民動員」參與了2016年的[[打擊恐怖主義行動|收復費盧杰]]行動，在費盧杰外圍作戰支援政府軍攻勢，為免引起遜尼派不安，「人民動員」表示不會參與攻城戰。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/first/20160531/19634379 |title=兵分三路圍剿 伊拉克軍攻入IS重鎮費盧杰 |work=蘋果日報 |location=香港 |date=2016-05-31 |accessdate=2016-06-12 |archive-date=2016-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161006055143/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/first/20160531/19634379 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

